entries.title_d: A face to face battle with a Black Sun Ace fighter named Crystal Snake
entries.title: Lok System: Assist the RSF Take down Crystal Snake
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy fighters are moving in on your position. Repeat, enemy fighters moving in on your  position. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_location_d: An area of the Lok System
entries.quest_helpallies_d: A trio of RSF Hunters, you fail the mission if they all die
entries.quest_findbattle_d: Travel here to set up the ambush
entries.found_loc: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Scanners show a second target in the area, travel to the following area.  Keep an eye out for a Black Sun operative named Crystal Snake. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.enemies_win: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 We needed that hunter group alive, this is unacceptable. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.enemies_remaining: An enemy craft has been destroyed, %DI remain.
entries.enemies_arrived: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft have entered normal space. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.battle_started: \#pcontrast3 Crystal Snake: < \#pcontrast1 Enjoy this moment RSF trash, it will be your last. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.allies_win: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Good work... wait, we are picking up something on scanners. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.allies_remaining: An allied craft has been destroyed, %DI remain.
entries.allies_arrived: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 We have sent a hunter squad to assist you for this mission.  It should not be a problem. \#pcontrast3 >
